      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">WATSON &amp; SCULL, ¶ Horticultural and General Forwarding Agents ¶ to all Parts of the World ¶ 90, Lower Thames Street, E. C. ¶ London, ¶  15 June 1880...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">M80.06.15</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Watson &amp; Scull to Ferdinand von Krauss</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Staatliches Museum für Naturkunde, Stuttgart.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">M's London Agents.</p>
               </note>WATSON &amp; SCULL,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Horticultural and General Forwarding Agents</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">to all Parts of the World</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">90, Lower Thames Street, E. C.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg>London,</seg> 15 June 1880</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Professor Dr. Krauss</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Stuttgard </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Dear Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>We have the pleasure to advise that we have this day forwarded to the care of Dr. W. Sonder, Papenstrasse, Hamburg, to forward on to you:</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>D. K. 1/3 Three Cases Specimens received from Stuttgard</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The Baron Fr. Von Mueller, Melbourne, which we trust will reach you safely —</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>These Cases <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">have not</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">been</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">opened at</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">all</hi>
               </seg> i<seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">n</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">London</hi>
               </seg>, so you should receive these valuable Specimen in the same condition that they left Melbourne, undisturbed. —</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>We take this opportunity to tender you our service for the forwarding of any goods you may have for India, Australia or any of the Colonies</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">We remain dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Yours truly</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Watson &amp; Scull </p>
         </div>
